Gnathosoma. Corniculi slightly convergent distally; basal width of corniculus 4 , distance between bases of corniculi 8 . Movable cheliceral digit 34 ( 33–34 ) long, apparently with three teeth; fixed digit 32 ( 31–32 ) long, apparently with 9–10 teeth; dorsal and lateral lyrifissures distinct (
